                    <br />
            <span class="comments">I&#39;m not sure I understand. If a player tries to kill another one <i>during an encounter</i>, either the GM cheats, or the target (or the whole party!) should most certainly die. How can this be going on for over 1 year without them becoming extinct?</span>
    </td>
